results.description: I usually don’t have much time to go and capture some wildlife. On this day, I decided to go to a little island called Seurasaari with my sister. It’s an island where many free and friendly squirrels run freely. If you’re lucky, you can see foxes, too. Didn’t see any foxes but got lucky enough to meet this little guy. I think I captured a perfect moment and I love the candidness of this picture. I do love nature and wildlife and will have to promise myself to capture it more often!
